210
00:16:13.931 --> 00:16:16.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Compartilharemos o que tivermos.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:16:17.059 --> 00:16:19.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>E compartilharemos o sofrimento.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:16:27.027 --> 00:16:29.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Harrow prometeu ajudar</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>além do que podíamos.</i></c.bg_transparent>

213
00:16:31.448 --> 00:16:33.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Naquele inverno, a fome e a morte,</i></c.bg_transparent>

214
00:16:34.493 --> 00:16:36.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>tragédias devastadoras...</i></c.bg_transparent>

215
00:16:37.913 --> 00:16:39.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>seriam inevitáveis.</i></c.bg_transparent>

216
00:16:41.417 --> 00:16:45.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Mas uma nova possibilidade</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>se apresentou a mim.</i></c.bg_transparent>

217
00:16:45.671 --> 00:16:48.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Andei pesquisando!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Dá para ver.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:16:51.260 --> 00:16:54.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estudei textos antigos, mapas e arquivos.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:16:54.430 --> 00:16:58.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>E posso ter encontrado...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>uma solução criativa.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:16:58.851 --> 00:17:01.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Algo que pode salvar vidas.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:17:01.186 --> 00:17:02.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bem, vá em frente.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:17:02.521 --> 00:17:03.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Observe!</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:17:05.024 --> 00:17:06.066 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>É uma pedra.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:17:06.483 --> 00:17:10.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Essa "pedra" é, na verdade,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>uma relíquia rara de Xadia.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:17:10.696 --> 00:17:12.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>É um pedaço de um monstro,</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:17:12.698 --> 00:17:15.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>um gigante de pedra</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que vive nas montanhas:</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:17:15.534 --> 00:17:17.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um titã de magma!</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:17:19.329 --> 00:17:21.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Está quente.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Sim.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:17:21.623 --> 00:17:24.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O titã vive perto da fronteira de Xadia.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:17:24.251 --> 00:17:26.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se pudermos caçar este monstro</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>e destruí-lo,</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:17:27.504 --> 00:17:29.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>posso usar o coração do titã</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:17:29.590 --> 00:17:32.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>num feitiço poderoso para aquecer a terra</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:17:32.301 --> 00:17:35.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>e nos permitir fazer crescer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>uma incrível recompensa.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:17:35.637 --> 00:17:37.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bastante para 2 reinos?</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:17:37.181 --> 00:17:38.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bastante para dez reinos!</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:17:40.434 --> 00:17:42.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>É claro, na época,</i></c.bg_transparent>

237
00:17:42.186 --> 00:17:45.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>eu não era o conselheiro</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>mais próximo ao rei.</i></c.bg_transparent>

238
00:17:51.528 --> 00:17:53.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Isso é um erro, Harrow!</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:17:53.322 --> 00:17:55.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Qual o seu problema com isso?</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:18:03.165 --> 00:18:06.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Matamos um monstro</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para salvar cem mil pessoas.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:18:06.335 --> 00:18:08.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fica o chamando de monstro.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:18:08.504 --> 00:18:11.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sim, é uma fera gigante de pedra e magma.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:18:11.465 --> 00:18:12.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chamo isso de monstro.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:18:19.556 --> 00:18:21.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Ele é inteligente?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-O quê?</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:18:21.934 --> 00:18:23.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Como assim?</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:18:23.268 --> 00:18:24.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ele pensa? Ele sente?</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:18:25.646 --> 00:18:27.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ele tem família?</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:18:29.066 --> 00:18:31.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Duvido muito que tenha família.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:18:31.527 --> 00:18:33.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Então é o último dos seus?</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:18:33.862 --> 00:18:35.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por que isso importa?</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:18:37.574 --> 00:18:40.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sei que parece que vai resolver tudo,</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:18:40.202 --> 00:18:42.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>mas isso não é muito fácil?</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:18:42.704 --> 00:18:44.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>É assim com a magia sombria.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:18:44.998 --> 00:18:46.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Que escolha nós temos?</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:18:52.381 --> 00:18:54.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Disse querer criar um mundo melhor,</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:18:54.550 --> 00:18:56.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>para mudar mesmo as coisas.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:18:56.260 --> 00:18:58.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mas levará décadas de trabalho duro.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:18:58.762 --> 00:19:02.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não pode matar monstros</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>e resolver todos os problemas.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:19:02.349 --> 00:19:04.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não há nenhum atalho!</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:19:05.394 --> 00:19:08.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Será um caminho perigoso!</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:19:10.649 --> 00:19:13.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Harrow, diga que não vai fazer isso!</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:19:15.112 --> 00:19:17.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>É nossa única chance.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:19:28.167 --> 00:19:30.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chegaremos a Xadia pela fenda.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:19:30.210 --> 00:19:32.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lá, pegaremos suprimentos e...</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:19:36.425 --> 00:19:37.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>estou aqui.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:19:37.467 --> 00:19:38.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rainha Sarai.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:19:42.347 --> 00:19:45.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Achei que desaprovasse.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Não concordo.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:19:46.018 --> 00:19:48.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mas... estou ao seu lado mesmo assim.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:19:49.062 --> 00:19:50.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Obrigado.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:19:50.355 --> 00:19:52.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Isso estava nos votos, né?</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:19:52.733 --> 00:19:56.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Algo sobre mantê-lo vivo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>quando agir feito um idiota corajoso?</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:19:59.823 --> 00:20:00.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vamos.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:20:06.079 --> 00:20:08.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Viajamos o mais rápido possível</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>para a fronteira.</i></c.bg_transparent>

274
00:20:09.249 --> 00:20:11.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Aventureiros corajosos dos dois reinos</i></c.bg_transparent>

275
00:20:11.960 --> 00:20:13.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>cruzaram a fenda juntos,</i></c.bg_transparent>

276
00:20:14.046 --> 00:20:16.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>esperando achar</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>uma forma de ajudar seu povo.</i></c.bg_transparent>

277
00:20:20.052 --> 00:20:24.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Trovão, o rei dos dragões patrulha</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>os céus da madrugada até o crepúsculo.</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:20:24.431 --> 00:20:26.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Entraremos em Xadia ao pôr do sol,</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:20:27.100 --> 00:20:29.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>e voltaremos com o coração do titã</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:20:29.228 --> 00:20:31.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>antes que se inicie o nascer do sol.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:20:31.813 --> 00:20:34.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Essas balistas derrubarão</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>um titã de magma?</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:20:34.816 --> 00:20:36.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se nosso alvo for real,</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:20:36.568 --> 00:20:39.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>acharemos o lugar certo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>e conseguiremos.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:20:46.161 --> 00:20:47.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O quê?</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:20:48.247 --> 00:20:49.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nada.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:21:07.015 --> 00:21:10.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Entramos na escuridão e logo</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>começamos o trabalho.</i></c.bg_transparent>

287
00:21:37.337 --> 00:21:39.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vamos! A noite é curta.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:21:43.760 --> 00:21:46.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>A cada passo dentro de Xadia,</i></c.bg_transparent>

289
00:21:46.638 --> 00:21:49.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>meu coração batia mais alto</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>de euforia e medo.</i></c.bg_transparent>

290
00:21:49.975 --> 00:21:53.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Este lugar tinha a promessa</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>de nossa salvação</i></c.bg_transparent>

291
00:21:53.729 --> 00:21:56.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>e a ameaça de nossa destruição.</i></c.bg_transparent>

292
00:22:05.949 --> 00:22:08.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Estávamos prontos</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>para lutar por nossas vidas.</i></c.bg_transparent>

293
00:22:14.207 --> 00:22:15.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Achamos o titã...</i></c.bg_transparent>

294
00:22:16.126 --> 00:22:18.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>mas não era o que esperávamos.</i></c.bg_transparent>

295
00:22:19.838 --> 00:22:22.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Está morto! O que faremos agora?</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:22:22.924 --> 00:22:24.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não fique tão decepcionada.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:22:24.926 --> 00:22:27.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se morreu, não precisamos matá-lo.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:22:27.179 --> 00:22:28.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nós só...</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:22:28.472 --> 00:22:30.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>o abrimos e pegamos o necessário.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:22:57.334 --> 00:22:59.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tenho essa carta faz uns dias</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:22:59.169 --> 00:23:01.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>mas não consigo abri-la.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:23:02.005 --> 00:23:03.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sei que parece loucura,</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:23:03.965 --> 00:23:05.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>mas é como se, agora,</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:23:05.801 --> 00:23:07.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>fossem coisas que ele não pôde dizer.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:23:07.803 --> 00:23:09.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>E estão todas aqui.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:23:09.721 --> 00:23:11.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Só esperando para tomar vida.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:23:12.933 --> 00:23:14.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mas, quando eu as ler...</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:23:15.644 --> 00:23:17.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quando ler a última delas...</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:23:18.438 --> 00:23:20.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>então ele terá ido mesmo.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:23:21.108 --> 00:23:22.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Para sempre.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:23:26.655 --> 00:23:28.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Certo. Obrigado, Isca.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:24:49.446 --> 00:24:51.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Legendas: Lenise Fernandes</c.bg_transparent>

